  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>The <code>.sr-only</code> text is still visible. There is a common pattern to visually hide text for only screen readers to read.</p>\n<p>This pattern is to set the following CSS properties:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">position: absolute;\nwidth: 1px;\nheight: 1px;\npadding: 0;\nmargin: -1px;\noverflow: hidden;\nclip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);\nwhite-space: nowrap;\nborder: 0;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Use the above to define the <code>sr-only</code> class.</p>\n</section>",
